	(1,'1','1',0,'nosotros','about us','img/contents/d63045ed31efc7bd623814242b9b5f8a.jpg','<p>Resumen de quienes somos</p>\n','<p>We provide premium Web Development and Web Design solutions in around the world. Our company provides professional websites that are strategically branded and mobile-friendly with responsive web design for organizations looking to grow their online business by having static, dynamic, e-Commerce, or CMS-based websites.</p>\n\n<p>We create all kinds of website for all purposes with usability, powerful scalability, and search engine optimization in mind. We inspire you for better branding that drives business growth using boosting features and awesome design.&nbsp;</p>\n','<p>cuerpo de quienes somos</p>\n','<p>Our company delivers scalable &amp; suitable digital solutions for small and big businesses. We love new challenges and we have a rare blend of both design, and development expertise that gives us the capabilities of building some complex and custom web features for our clients.</p>\n\n<p>With expertise spanning modern websites, e-commerce, video production, and mobile-responsive front-end design, our clients can enjoy the full spectrum of digital services from a single agency partner.</p>\n\n<p>We guarantee you getting more from the website using high value web features and by creating a better user experience that improves conversions and adapts the website to meet your needs of your online gate.</p>\n\n<h3><span style=\"color:#6a8f30\">Dynamic Websites for all purposes</span></h3>\n\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width:100%\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<ul>\n				<li>e-Commerce Websites</li>\n			</ul>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<ul>\n				<li>Real Estate Finder Websites</li>\n			</ul>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<ul>\n				<li>Job Portals Websites</li>\n			</ul>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<ul>\n				<li>University Websites</li>\n			</ul>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<ul>\n				<li>Education Centre Websites</li>\n			</ul>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<ul>\n				<li>Auto Showroom Websites</li>\n			</ul>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<ul>\n				<li>Events Organizers websites</li>\n			</ul>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<ul>\n				<li>Medical Centre Websites</li>\n			</ul>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<ul>\n				<li>Tours Booking Websites</li>\n			</ul>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<ul>\n				<li>Online Magazine Websites</li>\n			</ul>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h3><span style=\"color:#6a8f30\">What we think ​</span></h3>\n\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width:100%\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1/websarrollo/img/about_01.png\" style=\"height:132px; width:132px\" /></td>\n			<td style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1/websarrollo/img/about_02.png\" style=\"height:132px; width:132px\" /></td>\n			<td style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1/websarrollo/img/about_03.png\" style=\"height:132px; width:132px\" /></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Responsive Design</strong></span></td>\n			<td style=\"text-align:center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Easy to Customize</span></strong></td>\n			<td style=\"text-align:center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Unlimited Flexibility</span></strong></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"text-align:center\">A website that is fully optimized for tablets and mobile devices</td>\n			<td style=\"text-align:center\">We build powerful CMS-based websites where you can edit content easily</td>\n			<td style=\"text-align:center\">Super flexible websites for all purposes, aiming to grow your business</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h3><span style=\"color:#6a8f30\">5 Steps to get your website done with us</span></h3>\n\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width:100%\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong><em>1. First Meeting &amp; Discussion</em></strong></span></td>\n			<td><strong><em>2. Planning &amp; Research</em></strong></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>A coffee, a pencil, and a white paper. Discussion about your website purpose, goals, target audience, and content.</p>\n\n			<p>Here we clarify a brief image about the nature of work and style, then we write down inputs and suggestions about your project.</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>Using the information gathered from step #1, it is time to put together a plan for your web site. This is the point where a site map is developed.</p>\n\n			<p>We will list all main topic areas of the site, as well as scales, timelines, technology to be used.</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><em><strong>3. Proposing a Solution</strong></em></td>\n			<td><em><strong>4. Design &amp; Development</strong></em></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>According to the discussion in step #1, and the plan in step #2, we will propose a solution that fits your requirements. &nbsp;</p>\n\n			<p>Now; ideas are visibly structured into a proposed project, so we will design a proper layout for your expected website.</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>In this step, communication between us and you is close to ensure that the final website will match your needs and taste. &nbsp;</p>\n\n			<p>Here we start developing your website with passion using various web programming languages and web technologies &amp; elements.</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><em><strong>5. Testing &amp; Delivery</strong></em></td>\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Congratulations! You are almost Done. At this point, we come to the final review &amp; test for your expected website in order to launch it live for public audience.</td>\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n','izodiac','0','2015-01-31 02:01:47',NULL),
